# AI Voice Assistance (TTS) — Walkthrough

## What Was Built

Browser-native Text-to-Speech for all AI responses, using the Web Speech API (`SpeechSynthesis`). Zero latency, zero cost, no API keys or server changes needed.

## Files Changed

| File | Action | Purpose |
|------|--------|---------|
| [useTextToSpeech.ts](file:///d:/Projects/Consensus_HK/frontend/src/hooks/useTextToSpeech.ts) | **NEW** | React hook wrapping SpeechSynthesis: `speak()`, `stop()`, voice selection, markdown/emoji stripping, localStorage toggle persistence |
| [VoiceToggle.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/Consensus_HK/frontend/src/components/ai/VoiceToggle.tsx) | **NEW** | Polished toggle button with speaking-wave animation, compact & full variants |
| [useAI.ts](file:///d:/Projects/Consensus_HK/frontend/src/hooks/useAI.ts) | **MODIFIED** | Integrated TTS — `tts.speak()` called after every bot message, `tts` exposed on return |
| [ChatPanel.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/Consensus_HK/frontend/src/components/ai/ChatPanel.tsx) | **MODIFIED** | Voice toggle rendered in input bar next to "Clear chat" |
| [assistant.tsx](file:///d:/Projects/Consensus_HK/frontend/src/pages/assistant.tsx) | **MODIFIED** | Voice toggle in page header, `tts` passed to ChatPanel |

## How It Works

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    User->>useAIChat: sendMessage("What is a market?")
    useAIChat->>API: POST /api/ai/chat
    API-->>useAIChat: { message: "A prediction market is..." }
    useAIChat->>ChatPanel: addMessage({ type: 'bot', content })
    useAIChat->>useTextToSpeech: tts.speak(content)
    useTextToSpeech->>Browser: SpeechSynthesisUtterance
    Browser-->>User: 🔊 Voice plays
```

## Key Design Decisions

- **Web Speech API** — native browser TTS, no third-party service needed
- **Non-blocking** — `speak()` is fire-and-forget, never blocks the chat
- **Smart text cleaning** — strips `**bold**`, emoji, hex addresses, URLs before speaking
- **Voice preference** — auto-selects Google/Microsoft English voices for quality
- **Persistent toggle** — saved to `localStorage` so the setting survives page reloads

