## Manual Testing

Once the app is accessible (auth/DB issues resolved), test at `http://localhost:3000/assistant`:

1. Send a chat message → AI response appears AND is spoken aloud
2. Click "Voice Off" toggle → next response is silent
3. Click "Voice On" toggle → voice resumes
